---
// Shared site footer. Tool pages render their how-it-works + FAQ above this in
// ToolAboutCard / ToolFaqCard, so the footer itself is just the credit line.
---
<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-background)] p-6 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1080px] flex-col items-center gap-2">
    <p class="m-0 text-[0.85rem] text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      Built with ❤️ by <a class="font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shlomi Shemesh</a>.
      <span class="ml-2 inline-flex items-center gap-[0.4rem]">
        <a class="font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/shlomsh/pdkef" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> &bull;
        <a class="font-medium text-inherit no-underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:underline" href="/licenses">Licenses</a>
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
